components.value: It is the year 10193 in Arrakis.  This deserted planet is the only source of spice,  the key
to space travel, that has been found. War between the Atreides, who took on the
planetary fief by order of the emperor, and the Harkonnen,previous rulers of Arrakis.
This war has shaken the infinite dunes of the planet, and has resulted in the near
annihilation of the Atreides and reinstated the tyranny of the Harkonnen.
The Fremen, the true inhabitants of the planet, now face the Harkonnen alone.
One of the only Fremen cities that escaped the Harkonnen control is Sannara,
which location remains hidden by mirages, something that was about to change...
The current ruler of Arrakis, the tyrant Glossu Rabaan Harkonnen, the Beast,
was made aware of the possible loation of Sannara. Immediately establishing a camp
near the locaton he was ready to sieze the opportunity, the beast was ready for a bloodbth.
He had established a perimeter around the rock formation where Sannara
was established and had complete vision of the mirages that hid the Sietch.
The only ones capable of stopping this threat were the group of warriors that
form the spearhead from Sannara: Nerala, fiercest hunter in Arrakis, Omozra,
master of worms, and their head, Zhib, son of Zhiffat, blade of the desert.
Nerala was sent on a reconnaissance mission and reported that Rabban had made a mistake.  He was
there, in the camp, at her reach, and she was going to end the bloodshed right then and there.
She was going to kill him.
Fearing the dangers of this improvised mission, Zhib and Omozra decided to go after her
to stop her.
